subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Can Jeff Gordon rebound from a winless 2008 and perform as he did in 2007, when he won six races and gave Jimmie Johnson a run for the championship before finishing second?
